body.description: Furinno Turn-S-Tube No Tools Series multipurpose storage rack shelves comes in 2-3-4 Tiers and variety of width and depth. This series of products also includes difference sizes width, height and different fun colors. This series is designed to meet the demand of fits in space, fits on budget and yet durable and efficient furniture. It is proven to be the most popular RTA furniture due to its functionality, price, and the no hassle assembly. There are no screws involved, thus it is totally safe to be a family project. Just turn the tube to connect the panels to form a storage shelf. The materials comply with CARB grade particle board for furniture processed from parts of rubber trees. There is no foul smell of chemicals, durable and it is the most stable medium density composite wood used to make RTA furniture. Care instructions: Wipe clean with clean damped cloth. Avoid using harsh chemicals. Pictures are for illustration purpose. All decor items are not included in this offer.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: About the Manufacturer Bridging innovation with simplistic furniture, Furinno brings modern designs to transform your home into a one-of-a-kind oasis that will surely assist the compact and space saving need for your home. Engineered with recycled Malaysian rubberwood, Furinno is committed to making home furnishing easy affordable, and unique while remaining sustainable in the process. Furinno Turn-N-Tube Shoe Rack Series The Turn-n-Tube Shoe Rack Series is a contemporary line of shoe storage solutions known for its simplicity, efficiency, and easy assembly. Turn-n-Tube system relies on twisting the tubes, this makes setup a breeze even for those not accustomed to DIY furniture assembly. Modern color style. Stylish. Functional. Affordable. Easy to assemble.

Versatile Meets Stylish The elegant two-tier design shoe rack offers additional space for accessories. Easy & Fast Assembly Assembly is made easy by twisting the tubes against the panels. This shoe rack features open shelves for storing up to 9 pairs of shoes. Added Feature Designed with rounded edges for added safety to reduce accidental injury. Premium Quality Materials Manufactured from high quality particle board for long product life span and durability.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great shoe rack
reviews.reviewText: Easy to assemble and the perfect size for my hall closet. The edges of the shelves were a bit rough in spots, but as it was going in a closet, it didn't bother me.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Nice shoe rack, but they should have made it a bit wider.
reviews.reviewText: Nice shoe rack, looks good and easy to put together! The only issue is that 3 pairs of shoes really dont fit on each unless they are skinny like women's heels. I was able to get 3 pairs on the top, but they hang over a bit and are crooked on the top cap. So, it is really only good for 6 pairs, maybe more if they are skinny shoes. They should just make it a couple of inches wider!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Overall, great product. Did come damaged
reviews.reviewText: It looks great and feels sturdy. SUPER simple to put together! One corner was damaged though. I made sure that piece was on the bottom.
